    Consider the function <m>f(x)=\sqrt{4-x^2}</m>. Notice that on the domain <m>[-2,2]</m>, the shape formed between the graph and the <m>x</m>-axis is a semicircle. What is <m>\int_{-2}^2 f(x) \, dx</m>?</p>
